data.description: Back on the market! Priced to sell! Welcome to this home tucked away on a quaint block in the heart of Fishtown. This home offers a living room and separate dining area and two nice sized bedrooms. The yard is a nice size with a patio that is perfect for entertaining. Right around the corner from you are Fishtown Crossing, Starbucks, Loco Pez, Cedar Point and Medusa. Everything that Fishtown has to offer is just a short walk. Come take a look, move in and make it your own. This is a short sale. Short sale is approved by bank. Contact agent for further details.
